{"title":"GCM","uid":"17123eb273eb28de4ba456a5c252cb7a","slug":"git/credential-manager","date":"2023-10-28T15:09:09.608Z","updated":"2024-03-20T07:50:50.270Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/git/credential-manager.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/28/28tyr5UZbIVm7wX.png","content":"<p><a href=\"https://github.com/git-ecosystem/git-credential-manager/blob/main/docs/multiple-users.md\">git凭据管理(git-credential-manager)-多用户</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"帮助命令\"><a href=\"#帮助命令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"帮助命令\"></a>帮助命令</h3><div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki nord\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">git</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">credential-manager</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">github</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">--help</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #616E88\"># Description:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #616E88\">#   Commands for interacting with the GitHub host provider</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #616E88\"># </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #616E88\"># Usage:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #616E88\">#   git-credential-manager github [command] [options]</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #616E88\"># </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #616E88\"># Options:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #616E88\">#   --no-ui         Do not use graphical user interface prompts</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #616E88\">#   -?, -h, --help  Show help and usage information</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #616E88\"># </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #616E88\"># Commands:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #616E88\">#   list              List all known GitHub accounts.</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #616E88\">#   login             Add a GitHub account.</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #616E88\">#   logout &lt;account&gt;  Remove a GitHub account.</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"查看凭据列表\"><a href=\"#查看凭据列表\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"查看凭据列表\"></a>查看凭据列表</h3><div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki nord\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">git</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">credential-manager</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">github</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">list</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #616E88\"># kidwen</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #616E88\"># levy</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"删除用户凭据\"><a href=\"#删除用户凭据\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"删除用户凭据\"></a>删除用户凭据</h3><div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki nord\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #88C0D0\">git</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">credential-manager</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">github</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">logout</span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">levy</span></span></code></pre></div>","text":"git凭据管理(git-credential-manager)-多用户 帮助命令bashgit credential-manager github --help...","permalink":"/post/git/credential-manager","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":629,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"GIT","slug":"GIT","count":1,"path":"api/categories/GIT.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"git","slug":"git","count":2,"path":"api/tags/git.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B8%AE%E5%8A%A9%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">帮助命令</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E5%87%AD%E6%8D%AE%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">查看凭据列表</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E5%87%AD%E6%8D%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">删除用户凭据</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Kidwen","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/38277891?v=4","link":"/","description":"Frontend","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/kidwen","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"angular time format","uid":"d270d462daf0496aec69d3ecc94557ef","slug":"frontend/angular-time","date":"2023-11-21T09:27:56.038Z","updated":"2024-03-19T09:28:27.634Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/frontend/angular-time.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://s2.loli.net/2023/11/21/jRFKdD7oT4yC5kg.png","text":"Angular 拥有强悍的时间格式化管道以及方法，本文主要介绍formatDate方法的使用。 引入typescriptimport &#123; format...","permalink":"/post/frontend/angular-time","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"ANGULAR","slug":"ANGULAR","count":5,"path":"api/categories/ANGULAR.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"angular","slug":"angular","count":5,"path":"api/tags/angular.json"},{"name":"time fo